items.name: Messi_or_Ronaldo
items.description: This project analyzes the data of Lionel Messi and Cristiano Ronaldo during the 2008-2016 seasons. Setting aside marketing-driven awards and grand football narratives, it focuses solely on the most consistent and routine competitive performance of Messi and Ronaldo from a league perspective.
